25:54.583 --> 25:58.208
I don't remember
ever feeling so alive.

25:58.291 --> 26:03.250
And so, okay, it also means
feeling this terrible pain.

26:03.333 --> 26:04.667
It's part of the deal.

26:11.667 --> 26:13.834
You're really
suffering though, honey.

26:14.709 --> 26:15.834
Hmm.

26:17.500 --> 26:19.000
What would be better?

26:20.208 --> 26:21.458
