with Peter.

26:23.625 --> 26:25.041
-MIRA: I know.
-Yeah.

26:26.291 --> 26:28.291
Does that seem
reasonable to you?

26:28.375 --> 26:30.792
Life without any passion,
right? Kind of like--

26:30.875 --> 26:33.667
Well, passion, okay,
it's awesome,

26:33.750 --> 26:35.959
uh, but, you know,
it's not sustainable.

26:36.041 --> 26:37.417
We're not 16 anymore.
You can't--

26:37.500 --> 26:38.792
What does 16
have to do with anything?

26:38.875 --> 26:40.417
Did you renounce passion
at the age of 16?

26:40.500 --> 26:42.250
No, I'm not saying
that I renounced it.

26:42.333 --> 26:43.917
KATE: Don't start quoting
Jonathan's theories

26:44.000 --> 26:46.542
-about marriage.
-I'm not quoting him.

26:46.625 --> 26:51.375
