this open relationship

26:51.458 --> 26:53.959
-comes at a price for everybody.
-Of course it does.

26:54.041 --> 26:57.250
And... it can't be easy
for your kids, right?

26:59.542 --> 27:03.166
Well, it's not easy
for any kid, Mira.

27:03.250 --> 27:04.458
I mean...

27:07.375 --> 27:10.458
Honestly, in the long run,
I think that it's actually...

27:11.417 --> 27:12.959
very empowering for them

27:13.041 --> 27:17.041
to see me always searching
for freedom and happiness.

27:18.875 --> 27:21.583
I don't know,
self-actualization?

27:24.000 --> 27:26.458
It's absolutely something
that I want to model for them.

27:27.417 --> 27:28.750
Especially Anna.

27:32.834 --> 27:34.125
Okay.

27:37.083 --> 27:39.208
I'm not judging you, honey.
I'm not.

27:39.291 --> 27:40.291
Yeah.

27:42.917 --> 27:45.667
MIRA: And I'm on your side
always. You know that, right?

27:47.333 --> 27:49.125
I know. I do.

27:51.625 --> 27:53.375
I'm sorry. Here.

27:53.458 --> 27:56.083
-Mm.
-KATE: No, no, no.

27:56.166 --> 27:58.291
(KATE EXHALES SHAKILY)

28:00.125 --> 28:01.583
KATE: Hmm.

28:01.667 --> 28:02.959
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

28:03.041 --> 28:06.792
Oh, this day. It's just, like,
it's so much. It's...

28:10.041 --> 28:11.625
Wait, is something wrong?

28:14.125 --> 28:15.959
No, it's just, uh...

28:18.291 --> 28:21.250
It's just a lot of pressure, so.

28:22.125 --> 28:23.667
What kind of pressure?

28:26.667 --> 28:29.000
No, it's nothing. Forget it.

28:33.875 --> 28:35.667
(LAUGHS) What?

28:37.458 --> 28:40.625
Nothing, I just--
I'm sorry I lost it.

28:40.709 --> 28:43.041
(LAUGHS)

28:43.125 --> 28:45.709
I think it's okay.
That was crazy.

28:46.834 --> 28:47.834
KATE: Girl.

28:49.542 --> 28:52.667
-You're such a good friend. Hey.
-Aw.

28:53.458 --> 28:54.709
And you're stunning.

29:11.000 --> 29:12.208
KATE: I don't... (LAUGHS)

29:12.291 --> 29:14.625
-Not sure where what came from.
-(LAUGHS NERVOUSLY)

29:14.709 --> 29:16.375
KATE: I think I'm pretty drunk.

29:19.208 --> 29:20.375
MIRA: Um...

29:21.750 --> 29:23.583
-KATE: Okay. You good?
-Yeah.

29:23.667 --> 29:26.041
-Do you wanna go downstairs?
-Okay.

29:26.125 --> 29:30.000
-Mm. Yeah.
-(MIRA LAUGHS)

29:31.709 --> 29:32.625
KATE: Hang on.

29:32.709 --> 29:34.041
-Okay, come on.
-KATE: Okay.

29:35.125 --> 29:36.375
