33:29.792 --> 33:31.000
Sorry I left you down there.

33:31.083 --> 33:32.291
It's okay, sweetie.

33:33.000 --> 33:36.083
I couldn't take it anymore.

33:36.166 --> 33:38.125
JONATHAN: Yeah,
he was really drunk.

33:38.208 --> 33:39.375
MIRA: It was tragic.

33:39.458 --> 33:40.792
JONATHAN: Tragic, why?

33:40.875 --> 33:41.875
Why?

33:41.959 --> 33:44.125
Yeah. It's not like we
haven't seen that before.

33:46.542 --> 33:47.500
(SPITS)

33:47.583 --> 33:49.208
MIRA: She's really suffering.
I'm telling you.

33:49.291 --> 33:50.959
JONATHAN: Yeah,
I could see that, but--

33:51.041 --> 33:53.000
The sad thing is they're
basically a good couple

33:53.083 --> 33:55.875
if he hadn't roped her in
all his adolescent bullshit.

33:55.959 --> 33:57.125
JONATHAN: Yeah?

33:58.041 --> 34:00.083
You sure it's him
that roped her?

34:00.166 --> 34:02.250
Oh, come on.
It's not who she is,

34:02.333 --> 34:05.000
-this whole polyamory thing.
-(GARGLES)

34:06.250 --> 34:07.834
I think they both get to...

34:08.917 --> 34:10.667
feed off of the drama,
you know?

34:10.750 --> 34:13.792
Mm. Well, you get a kick
out of it, don't you?

34:14.959 --> 34:18.458
You must admit, darling,
it is diverting.

34:18.542 --> 34:21.000
MIRA: (CHUCKLES)
Whatever.

34:26.542 --> 34:29.166
♪ (MUSIC CONTINUES) ♪

35:13.417 --> 35:15.375
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪

35:36.000 --> 35:37.250
(SIGHS)

35:40.417 --> 35:41.583
What is it?

35:44.917 --> 35:46.709
Oh, don't look so scared.

35:46.792 --> 35:47.875
I'm not.

35:48.917 --> 35:50.250
What's going on?

35:55.917 --> 35:57.041
I'm pregnant.

35:59.291 --> 36:00.917
-What?
-Yeah.

36:04.291 --> 36:05.625
Wow.

36:07.875 --> 36:09.000
Mira.

36:11.208 --> 36:12.250
How?

36:13.125 --> 36:16.834
Uh, well, that weekend.
The Cape.

36:16.917 --> 36:19.291
Yeah, I forgot my pills,
so I missed a couple days.

36:19.375 --> 36:21.125
Why didn't you tell me
you forgot your pills?

36:21.208 --> 36:22.667
Well, I didn't think
that it mattered if we...

36:22.750 --> 36:26.041
Well, it shouldn't be so easy
to get knocked up at my age.

36:26.125 --> 36:27.375
(CHUCKLES)

36:27.458 --> 36:28.625
I took a...

36:28.709 --> 36:30.208
Well, I was late for my period,

36:30.291 --> 36:33.917
so I took a test this afternoon,
and there was a faint blue line.

36:34.000 --> 36:35.667
Okay, so it's a faint line,
so maybe...

36:35.750 --> 36:37.250
No, I took a picture
of the stick

36:37.333 --> 36:39.709
and sent it to my doctors.

36:39.792 --> 36:41.959
I'm pregnant. (LAUGHS)

36:42.041 --> 36:43.750
-Wow.
-Yeah.

36:44.625 --> 36:46.083
-Wow.
-Yeah. I've got an appointment

36:46.166 --> 36:48.166
with her next week. Dr. Varona.

36:48.667 --> 36:49.834
Okay.

36:53.375 --> 36:56.375
-Are you happy? Yeah?
-Yes, of course. I'm happy. Yes.

36:56.458 --> 36:58.417
I'm just a little-- I'm stunned.

36:58.500 --> 36:59.917
God, me too. (LAUGHS)

37:00.000 --> 37:03.166
I mean,
I have no idea what to do.

37:03.250 --> 37:04.625
What do you mean?

37:04.709 --> 37:07.542
Nothing. Nothing.
I just-- I don't know. It's...

37:10.000 --> 37:13.917
If we do this,
so much is gonna fall on you.

37:14.000 --> 37:16.500
(CLEARS THROAT) Yeah. Yeah.

37:18.125 --> 37:19.542
So, what do you feel?

37:21.583 --> 37:23.542
Well, I don't know.
I wanted to know how you felt.

37:23.625 --> 37:25.750
No, no, forget about me
for a second.

37:25.834 --> 37:27.083
What do you feel?

37:27.542 --> 37:28.875
(CLEARS THROAT)

37:30.875 --> 37:32.000
I don't know.

37:33.083 --> 37:35.041
-(LAUGHS)
-JONATHAN: Okay.

37:35.125 --> 37:38.291
Well, try to think about
how you felt

37:38.375 --> 37:40.041
the second that you realized.

37:40.959 --> 37:42.375
-Try to remember.
-Fine.

37:42.875 --> 37:45.208
I felt shocked.

37:45.291 --> 37:47.542
And, um, then I had to...

37:48.542 --> 37:50.208
come downstairs
for that interview,

37:50.291 --> 37:52.333
so I buried it. And now...

37:53.375 --> 37:54.583
I guess I...

37:58.125 --> 37:59.125
I don't know.

37:59.208 --> 38:00.500
JONATHAN: Come on.
You can be honest with me.

38:00.583 --> 38:01.917
Anything that you feel is
legitimate.

38:02.000 --> 38:03.041
I don't know how I feel.

38:03.125 --> 38:05.166
How am I supposed
to be honest about that?

38:06.583 --> 38:07.667
(CLEARS THROAT)

38:09.750 --> 38:10.792
MIRA: Sorry.

38:12.041 --> 38:15.583
Just trying to figure out
how this could have happened.

38:16.667 --> 38:17.709
Yeah.

38:19.208 --> 38:21.417
Maybe the sex
had something to do with it.

38:23.417 --> 38:26.125
(SIGHS) Yeah.

38:29.375 --> 38:32.959
Hey, what if-- what if we
think about this in,

38:33.041 --> 38:35.500
I don't know,
like a slightly more...

38:35.583 --> 38:37.750
(CLEARS THROAT)
...deterministic way?

38:37.834 --> 38:40.750
You know, like,
it's the Lord's doing, right?

38:40.834 --> 38:42.333
-What?
-Not in a religious sense.

38:42.417 --> 38:43.834
-Not in a religious sense.
-Okay.

38:43.917 --> 38:46.709
I just mean, like, I mean,
you know, okay,

38:46.792 --> 38:49.417
you forgot your pills.

38:49.750 --> 38:50.875
Uh-huh.

38:51.000 --> 38:52.417
And you still...?

38:53.583 --> 38:54.542
Yeah.

38:54.625 --> 38:56.250
JONATHAN: And you
immediately got pregnant.

38:56.333 --> 38:59.709
So is it possible that
there's a part of you that--

38:59.792 --> 39:03.083
wanted this or thought
that we should have this?

39:04.250 --> 39:06.709
Where is this coming from?

39:06.792 --> 39:09.375
-It's so...
-JONATHAN: I know, I know.

39:09.458 --> 39:11.208
I mean, if you're--
if you're trying to say

39:11.291 --> 39:13.458
that you want
to keep it, just say that.

39:13.542 --> 39:14.792
Well...

39:16.291 --> 39:17.417
I...

39:17.500 --> 39:19.291
I-- It's what we talked
about originally.

39:19.375 --> 39:21.875
Yeah. But originally,
it was completely abstract.

39:21.959 --> 39:23.458
I mean, it was...

39:23.542 --> 39:25.208
before we knew anything
about anything,

39:25.291 --> 39:26.291
it was before Ava,

39:26.375 --> 39:28.583
before we knew
what it was actually like.

39:33.500 --> 39:34.542
What?

39:40.542 --> 39:41.625
You...

39:43.250 --> 39:46.083
-You wanna keep it, right?
-I think so. Yeah, I think so.

39:46.166 --> 39:48.208
I think we can handle it,
but only if it's something

39:48.291 --> 39:50.709
that you really, really want
and would be happy about.

39:55.959 --> 39:57.041
I think so.

39:59.208 --> 40:00.625
I think I might.

40:02.583 --> 40:03.792
(JONATHAN COUGHS)

40:04.375 --> 40:05.834
Ava will be thrilled.

40:06.583 --> 40:08.709
-Yeah.
-(JONATHAN CHUCKLES)

40:09.834 --> 40:10.834
And your parents.

40:10.917 --> 40:13.542
Oh, God. (COUGHS) Yeah. Yeah.

40:19.083 --> 40:20.959
So, are we going for this?
Oh, my God.

40:21.041 --> 40:22.792
JONATHAN: Um...yeah?

40:22.875 --> 40:25.125
-(LAUGHING) Yeah.
-JONATHAN: Yeah. Come here.

40:25.208 --> 40:27.041
-Okay.
-Come here.

40:28.625 --> 40:31.542
(COUGHING)

40:32.375 --> 40:33.458
MIRA: You okay?

40:33.542 --> 40:36.542
(CONTINUES COUGHING)

40:37.125 --> 40:38.375
Here.

40:44.166 --> 40:45.875
(INHALES)

40:50.583 --> 40:52.333
(EXHALES) Don't...

40:53.083 --> 40:54.333
Don't look at me like that.

40:54.417 --> 40:55.875
This is--
this doesn't mean anything.

40:56.000 --> 40:57.250
-Right.
-(COUGHS)

40:57.333 --> 40:59.792
-It only means you're panicking.
-It doesn't mean I'm panicking.

40:59.875 --> 41:02.375
-I had a lot to drink.
-Yeah, hmm.

41:02.458 --> 41:04.792
But you know what, even if
I was panicking, so what?

41:04.875 --> 41:06.166
This is a really big deal, okay?

41:06.250 --> 41:08.250
This is irreversible,
what we're talking about here.

41:08.333 --> 41:10.583
-MIRA: Mm-hmm.
-(SIGHS)

41:11.250 --> 41:12.250
What?

41:15.458 --> 41:18.125
You know, it just sucks
that neither one of us

41:18.208 --> 41:22.250
